sequenceDiagram
    %% ==================== 通用页面加载流程 ====================
    title 通用页面加载流程（以招商代理中心为例）

    participant User as 用户
    participant Sidebar as Sidebar
    participant Router as React Router
    participant Layout as AgentLayout
    participant Page as AgentListPage
    participant Mock as useMockData
    participant UI as MUI组件

    User->>Sidebar: 点击「招商代理」
    Sidebar->>Router: navigate('/agent/list')
    Router->>Layout: 渲染 AgentLayout
    Layout->>Layout: 显示子页面Tab导航
    Router->>Page: 渲染 AgentListPage
    Page->>Mock: useAgentList()
    Mock-->>Page: Agent[] (useMemo缓存)
    Page->>Page: 搜索/过滤逻辑
    Page->>UI: 渲染SearchInput + FilterChips
    Page->>UI: 渲染AgentTable
    Note over Page,UI: 使用 ContentCard / StatsCard 等共享组件
    UI-->>User: 展示代理商列表

    User->>Page: 点击某代理商行
    Page->>UI: 打开AgentDetailDrawer
    Note over Page,UI: 抽屉展示代理详情/协议/结算记录
    UI-->>User: 展示代理商详情

    %% ==================== 佣金结算审核流程 ====================
    title 佣金结算审核流程

    participant Admin as 管理员
    participant SettlePage as SettlementListPage
    participant SettleTable as SettlementTable
    participant MockData as useSettlements

    Admin->>SettlePage: 访问佣金结算页面
    SettlePage->>MockData: useSettlements()
    MockData-->>SettlePage: CommissionSettlement[]
    SettlePage->>SettleTable: 渲染结算表格
    SettleTable-->>Admin: 展示结算列表（含状态标签）

    Admin->>SettleTable: 点击「审核」待结算单
    SettleTable->>SettleTable: 弹出审核确认框
    Note over SettleTable: 显示结算金额/佣金/订单明细
    Admin->>SettleTable: 确认审核通过
    SettleTable-->>Admin: 状态变更为「审核通过」

    %% ==================== 获客短视频创建流程 ====================
    title 短视频获客计划创建流程

    participant Operator as 运营人员
    participant VideoPage as ShortVideoPage
    participant VideoCard as VideoPlanCard
    participant Form as 创建表单

    Operator->>VideoPage: 访问短视频获客页面
    VideoPage->>VideoPage: useShortVideoPlans()
    VideoPage->>VideoCard: 渲染计划卡片列表
    VideoCard-->>Operator: 展示已发布/草稿计划
    Note over VideoCard: 显示播放量/点赞/线索数

    Operator->>VideoPage: 点击「新建计划」
    VideoPage->>Form: 打开创建表单
    Note over Form: 标题/平台/脚本/发布日期
    Operator->>Form: 填写信息并保存
    Form-->>VideoPage: 新增计划（草稿状态）
    VideoPage-->>Operator: 列表刷新

    %% ==================== 培训课程学习追踪流程 ====================
    title 培训课程学习与进度追踪

    participant Student as 学员
    participant CoursePage as CourseListPage
    participant CampPage as CampListPage
    participant ProgressPage as ProgressPage
    participant ProgressData as useStudentProgress

    Student->>CoursePage: 浏览课程中心
    CoursePage->>CoursePage: useCourses()
    CoursePage-->>Student: 课程卡片列表（含章节/进度）

    Student->>CampPage: 查看训练营
    CampPage->>CampPage: useTrainingCamps()
    CampPage-->>Student: 训练营列表及报名状态

    Student->>ProgressPage: 查看学习进度
    ProgressPage->>ProgressData: useStudentProgress()
    ProgressData-->>ProgressPage: StudentProgress[]
    ProgressPage-->>Student: 各课程/训练营完成进度

    %% ==================== 运营数据看板流程 ====================
    title 运营数据看板加载流程

    participant Manager as 运营经理
    participant DataPage as DataDashboardPage
    participant ChartCard as ChartCard
    participant KPIStats as KPIStatsRow
    participant DataMock as useOperationDashboards

    Manager->>DataPage: 访问运营看板
    DataPage->>DataMock: useOperationDashboards()
    DataMock-->>DataPage: OperationDashboard
    DataPage->>KPIStats: 渲染4个KPI指标
    KPIStats-->>Manager: 显示新增客户/签单额/活跃代理/投诉率
    DataPage->>ChartCard: 渲染收入趋势图（折线图）
    ChartCard-->>Manager: 显示月度收入趋势
    DataPage->>ChartCard: 渲染产品收入占比（饼图）
    ChartCard-->>Manager: 显示各产品版本收入占比
    DataPage->>ChartCard: 渲染转化漏斗（漏斗图）
    ChartCard-->>Manager: 显示获客到成交转化率

    %% ==================== 交付SOP查看流程 ====================
    title 交付SOP查看流程

    participant Staff as 交付人员
    participant SOPPage as SOPListPage
    participant SOPCard as SOPCard
    participant Timeline as SOPTimeline
    participant SOPData as useDeliverySOPs

    Staff->>SOPPage: 访问SOP管理
    SOPPage->>SOPData: useDeliverySOPs()
    SOPData-->>SOPPage: DeliverySOP[]
    SOPPage->>SOPCard: 渲染SOP分类卡片
    SOPCard-->>Staff: 显示SOP概览（标题/适用角色/天数）

    Staff->>SOPPage: 点击某SOP
    SOPPage->>Timeline: 渲染步骤时间线
    Note over Timeline: 展示stepOrder/描述/负责人/时长/交付物/检查项
    Timeline-->>Staff: 展开式时间线展示

    %% ==================== 任务依赖图流程 ====================
    title 开发依赖流程

    participant T01 as T01: 基础设施
    participant T02 as T02: Phase 1B
    participant T03 as T03: Phase 2
    participant T04 as T04: 集成1B
    participant T05 as T05: 集成2

    Note over T01: types + mockData + routes + navItems + constants
    T01->>T02: 类型定义就绪
    T01->>T03: 类型定义就绪
    Note over T02: 招商代理 + 获客引流 + 案例见证 + 培训赋能
    Note over T03: 交付服务 + 政策合同 + 品牌资产 + 数据运营
    T02->>T04: 页面组件就绪
    T03->>T05: 页面组件就绪
    Note over T04: 路由集成 + 导航激活 + 端到端验证
    Note over T05: 路由集成 + 导航激活 + 端到端验证
